The paper deals with vision-language understanding, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses supervised learning and attention mechanisms, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval, as it deals with linking different types of annotations, which is a task that falls under the scope of information retrieval (cs.IR).
